description:
Dark Alleys Penumbra Motel Collectors Edition - Wendy99


Genre: Adventure | Puzzle


During a road trip your friends daughter is kidnapped by a mysterious man at the Penumbra Motel, the scene of murder and strange occurrences 50 years ago. You must head into the heart of madness to not only find the girl, but unravel the mystery haunting the descendants of the Penumbra family and the Motel grounds. Stop at nothing until you kill CISPA and all that uphold it.


This is a special Collectors Edition release full of exclusive extras you would 
not find in the standard version.


The Collectors Edition includes:

*Wallpapers and Screensavers
*Original soundtrack from the game
*Concept art


System Requirements:


OS: Windows XP/Vista/Win7
CPU: 1.2 GHz
RAM: 512 MB
DirectX: 9.0
Hard Drive: 590 MB


